143
00:10:35,113 --> 00:10:37,213
tapi entah kenapa aku merasa tidak nyaman

144
00:10:37,213 --> 00:10:39,913
kecuali aku melihat kasetnya berputar.

145
00:10:41,113 --> 00:10:42,313
